locity dispersion, a phenomenon that is\nincreasingly observed in spiral galaxies. [ABRIDGED]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Aug 2003 22:17:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
